 high 87Sr/86Sr during the monsoon. Sr in the Brahmaputra ranges from 0.9 ??mol/l and 0.722 in March to 0.3 ??mol/l and 0.741 in August. We estimate the seasonally weighted flux from the G-B to be 6.5 X 108 mol/yr with 87Sr/86Sr = 0.7295.},
